blocks: 28  cells/block: 8-52  trials/block: 10-63
measured choice-to-movement correlation (realistic rho): 0.532
threshold signal injected: 0.24 SD per cell  (uncontrolled preserve-test AUC 0.584)

control     no-signal  preserve  retain  remove  valid
linear          0.489     0.607    1.26   0.508    yes
ridge           0.496     0.606    1.25   0.540    yes
pca             0.483     0.598    1.16   0.529    yes
expanded        0.497     0.540    0.48   0.491     no
